    <item>
      <title>Quotes Matter</title>
      <link>https://benmatselby.dev/tidbits/datadog/quotes-matter/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://benmatselby.dev/tidbits/datadog/quotes-matter/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I think this is probably always the case in many languages, but it caught me out&#xA;today (28th July 2025).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you have a log line that is something like like:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-text&#34; data-lang=&#34;text&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;ERR-ABC-123: Something went wrong&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Using terraform to show the error. If you use a &lt;code&gt;&#39;&lt;/code&gt; quote, it would match different things&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-terraform&#34; data-lang=&#34;terraform&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;resource&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;datadog_monitor&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;my_new_monitor&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  name    = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#24909d&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;.prefix&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;: Monitor for error&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  type    = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;log alert&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  query   = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;logs(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;env:test AND &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;ERR-ABC&lt;span style=&#34;color:#3677a9&#34;&gt;-123&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;).index(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;*&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;).rollup(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#24909d&#34;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;).last(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#3677a9&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;m&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2&#34;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;) &amp;gt; 0&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  message = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;my alert message&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  ...&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;So could match &lt;code&gt;ERR-A-123&lt;/code&gt; for example.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
